{
  "chapter": 41,
  "chapter_summary": "郭大路在济南府大明湖畔寻找燕七，终日游魂般在湖边徘徊。他在卖莲蓬的小姑娘处买莲蓬时，小姑娘悄悄告诉他，近两天有人一直在后面跟踪他——一个有时扮成小贩、有时扮成乞丐的大麻子。郭大路得知此人大概率是王动派来的人，心中一动。他故意对小姑娘编造自己是\"大盗满天飞\"、被名捕追踪的故事来逗她开心，小姑娘信以为真，兴奋得面红耳赤。郭大路戏弄完小姑娘后大笑离去，留下她满脸红霞怔在原地。这一章以轻松诙谐的笔调，展示了郭大路在寻找燕七途中偶遇村姑的趣事，同时暗示了神秘麻子一直在暗中跟踪他。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你过来，我有话跟你说。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你有什么话要跟我说？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你是不是化了装出来私访民情的大臣？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我由头到脚，有哪点像是大官的样子？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "不但不是，而且我一见到大官就会发抖的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "那么你一定是个大强盗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "也不是，我连做强盗都会蚀本的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你真的不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我为什么要骗你？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你从哪点看我像是个大盗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为这两天来，我总觉得有个人在后面盯你的梢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "哦，是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "这人有时打扮成小贩，有时打扮成乞丐，但无论他打扮成什么样子都休想瞒过我。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "因为他的脸我一眼就能够认出来，",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "他脸上是不是有与众不同的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他是个大麻子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他是不是来盯你梢的？你认不认得他？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我跟你说老实话，你可不许告诉别人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "我发誓不跟别人说，否则以后叫我也变成个大麻子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "好，我告诉你，那大麻是个很有名的捕头，的确是来盯我梢的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "他……他为什么要盯你的梢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "因为我的确是个大盗，别人都叫我'大盗满天飞'，刚在京城做了七十八件巨案，才逃到这里来避风头。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你……你是不是个采花盗？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你猜我是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "就算你是，我也不怕你，我……我……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你放心，我就算要来找你，也得再过两三年，现在你只不过还是个小孩子。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    }
  ],
